-Very good.

30:57.606 --> 30:59.440
-You computer literate?
-A little.

31:00.067 --> 31:01.067
Thelma!

31:01.777 --> 31:04.779
-Thelma? Where's my Thelma?
-Yes.

31:05.447 --> 31:07.698
Thelma, meet Amelia.
Amelia, Thelma.

31:07.950 --> 31:10.159
