32:00.669 --> 32:03.671
He's 79 with a tricky ticker
and an active pecker.

32:04.298 --> 32:05.506
Hey.

32:11.513 --> 32:13.889
-Afternoon. Captain Cheney.
-Amelia...

32:14.141 --> 32:15.891
...what about that asbestos?

32:16.143 --> 32:18.644
There's a dozen cleanups
in the five boroughs.

32:18.854 --> 32:20.521
Put it up on the viewer for me.

32:20.772 --> 32:23.441
Narrow it down
to the oldest locations.

32:23.692 --> 32:25.067
How you doing, Howie?

32:25.360 --> 32:26.736
Fine. How's it going?

32:27.029 --> 32:29.447
In the middle of the middle,
as you can see.

32:30.198 --> 32:33.284
Look what l found on
the threading of that iron bolt.

32:34.911 --> 32:37.455
I was hoping to grab a minute
if you don't mind.

32:38.582 --> 32:39.665
Excuse me.

32:39.958 --> 32:41.375
Sorry. Sorry.

32:42.044 --> 32:45.880
We got Donaghy to thank for
photographing the crucial evidence.

32:46.089 --> 32:47.757
Crucial evidence?

32:47.966 --> 32:52.887
We don't know that. l wanted to make
sure you had the support you need.

32:53.305 --> 32:57.558
I'm putting the full resources of
my department here at your disposal.

32:57.893 --> 32:59.935
I appreciate it. Thank you.

33:00.187 --> 33:01.979
But the thing is, Linc...

33:02.564 --> 33:06.609
...l've formalized procedures
since you were in charge, and so--

33:06.902 --> 33:09.403
Put what you got up
on my screen, please.

33:10.238 --> 33:13.074
So l'd appreciate it
if you kept me in the loop.

33:13.241 --> 33:14.784
Absolutely.

33:15.243 --> 33:16.619
At all times.

33:17.204 --> 33:18.454
At all--

33:18.747 --> 33:21.207
What the hell is that
we're looking at?

33:23.335 --> 33:24.919
Old paper.

33:25.420 --> 33:26.921
Coarse grade.

33:27.422 --> 33:28.756
I'd say...

33:28.965 --> 33:30.758
...80, 90 years old.

33:31.009 --> 33:33.719
Turn-of-the-century, it looks like.

33:35.430 --> 33:37.431
The perp likes old.

33:37.599 --> 33:39.100
Fine, then....

33:39.309 --> 33:41.435
I'll be in my office if you need me.

33:41.978 --> 33:43.145
Yeah, okay, Howie.

33:43.939 --> 33:44.939
Good.

33:48.777 --> 33:50.277
Old paper.

33:51.154 --> 33:52.613
Old gun.

33:54.616 --> 33:58.452
Buries his victim in a vintage
Civil War railroad bed.

33:59.621 --> 34:00.788
Sand.

34:02.332 --> 34:05.543
Sand. Sand....
Eddie, what do you got on the sand?

34:06.503 --> 34:09.797
