at personal reasons.

01:01:17.424 --> 01:01:18.758
Okay.

01:01:19.509 --> 01:01:22.511
Doesn't have anything to do
with your father, does it?

01:01:29.686 --> 01:01:31.479
You keep charging at walls.

01:01:31.772 --> 01:01:33.898
