any homicides in the last 1 2 months...

01:18:13.105 --> 01:18:16.858
...involving surgically-removed flesh
exposing bone.

01:18:18.152 --> 01:18:19.778
No problem.

01:18:20.780 --> 01:18:23.114
-See you soon.
-Hope so, Eddie.

